article_title: Here's What Health Insurance Consolidation Could Mean For Your Premiums

article_metadata.description: If you like high prices, then you probably hate marketplace competition. Nothing disrupts the normal relationship between supply and demand better than a monopoly. If you doubt that, look at your local cable bill. But in healthcare, competition doesn’t necessarily affect prices the way it does in other parts of the [...]
